value.name: Armed suspect shot by police outside Georgetown McDonald’s has died
value.description: That’s when officers shot the suspect. He’s been identified as 31-year-old DeShund Tanner. Tanner was taken to UK Hospital where he later died. Police say no officers or bystanders were hurt ...

value.description: Kentucky State Police said a suspect was shot and killed ... The Fayette County coroner has identified the man as 31-year-old DeShund Tanner. Like us on Facebook to see similar stories Please ...
